    "title": "Greaves Cotton is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Senior)",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Quality Control Engineer looking for your next big career move? Greaves Cotton in Jaipur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Greaves Cotton:\nGreaves Cotton is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Greaves Cotton!",
